title: Collapse Under The Empire
description:
My collection of Collapse Under The Empire. This collection includes all Studio Albums and most of their EPs and Singles. All files run at 320kbps mp3 except for one single file. The list of Albums, EPs and Singles follows.

4 Studio Albums
- Systembreakdown - (2009)
- Find A Place To Be Safe - (2010)
- Shoulders & Giants - (2011)
- Fragments Of A Prayer - (2012)

2 EPs
- The Sirens Sound - (2010)
- Black Moon Empire - (2011) - C.U.T.E. & Mooncake

Singles
- Crawling - (2009)
- Grade Separation -(2010)
- The Silent Death - (2011)
- Dragonfly - (2012)

Please seed whenever possible so everyone can enjoy this great music.
